# Vulnerabilities in @xmldom/xmldom bundled with the npm CLI shipped inside
# the Chainguard node base image at /usr/lib/node_modules/npm/node_modules/.
# The runtime container's CMD invokes node directly (e.g. `node api.js`); npm
# is never executed in the running container, so this code path is unreachable
# in production. Will remove these once Node.js bumps its bundled npm version.
